  {
    "row": 97,
    "rowsha": "nbzJ5Fek+lqGVHPv08Ff1Wh7A8KQ8vYkfUjGSaXJnpY=",
    "originContent": "## The Write Gate",
    "translatedContent": "## 書き込みゲート"
  },
  {
    "row": 98,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 99,
    "rowsha": "PWSYd7W4sNbE/NxaD/rmm2YKhv5sUStGOa4p09PFW7E=",
    "originContent": "This is the core idea. Before anything gets promoted to permanent memory, it has to pass at least one of these checks:",
    "translatedContent": "これが核心的な考え方です。何かが恒久的なメモリに昇格される前に、少なくとも以下のチェックのどれかを通過しなければなりません："
  },
  {
    "row": 100,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 101,
    "rowsha": "XfUrX+NJ6ME153a2xmsg91EzTsybBFAIrpaPqO6xwkg=",
    "originContent": "1. **Will it change how Claude behaves next time?** (a preference, a boundary, a pattern)",
    "translatedContent": "1. **次回のクロードの振る舞いを変えるか？**（好み、境界線、パターン）"
  },
  {
    "row": 102,
    "rowsha": "iCApm+2W1X8McMHI3/VB8z2QFnfd4JegoMV/CezkeL0=",
    "originContent": "2. **Is it a commitment someone's counting on?** (a deadline, a deliverable, a follow-up)",
    "translatedContent": "2. **誰かが頼りにしている約束か？**（締め切り、成果物、フォローアップ）"
  },
  {
    "row": 103,
    "rowsha": "CxphoEjOJS9fKvVt0U7PkuzkLWjBRq8FLQWDyTWtjPg=",
    "originContent": "3. **Is it a decision worth remembering the reasoning for?** (why you picked X over Y)",
    "translatedContent": "3. **理由を覚えておく価値のある決定か？**（なぜXを選んだかなど）"
  },
  {
    "row": 104,
    "rowsha": "d62twwZlsA2O+N2AR7T38W6EkjLdWbOZXjx0A1JxXNY=",
    "originContent": "4. **Is it a stable fact that'll come up again?** (not something that'll be different tomorrow)",
    "translatedContent": "4. **安定した事実でまた現れるか？**（明日には変わらないもの）"
  },
  {
    "row": 105,
    "rowsha": "O1K03SkZlyyw3nXeVJCJaWJWgM7RRex+ayFRHwQZoHE=",
    "originContent": "5. **Did you explicitly say \"remember this\"?**",
    "translatedContent": "5. **「これを覚えて」と明確に言ったか？**"
  },
  {
    "row": 106,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 107,
    "rowsha": "Z+IortAcHG0xYRswjyQkqxRlDuXle+sQ8uhE8mhiC7w=",
    "originContent": "If none of those are true, it stays in the daily notebook and eventually ages out. This keeps memory lean. No junk drawer.",
    "translatedContent": "これらのどれも当てはまらなければ、日誌に留まり、やがて期限切れになります。これでメモリがスリムに保たれます。不要な引き出しはなし。"
  },
  {
    "row": 108,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 109,
    "rowsha": "mF6Dx1gWiJiW+jhs8BTaYhbPHw3MNEHdsmjVyMfe/bA=",
    "originContent": "## When Corrections Happen",
    "translatedContent": "## 訂正が起こるとき"
  },
  {
    "row": 110,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 111,
    "rowsha": "mEw1dcAOaQMsSepbaqBzzhsJqbIfKIp26OC9QqucA3E=",
    "originContent": "If you tell Claude it got something wrong, it doesn't just say \"sorry\" and move on. It updates the daily notebook, the relevant register, and the counter, all in one shot. The old information gets marked as superseded (not deleted) so there's a trail of what changed and when.",
    "translatedContent": "クロードに間違いを指摘すると、ただ「すみません」と言って終わるのではありません。日誌、該当するレジスター、カウンターを一度に更新します。古い情報は削除されずに置き換え済みとしてマークされ、何がいつ変わったかの記録が残ります。"
  },
  {
    "row": 112,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 113,
    "rowsha": "SRRPf6YIchuC3ICjxgB/qPvsDLfLvarbDI/+dS/2xLI=",
    "originContent": "## What Loads Automatically",
    "translatedContent": "## 自動的に読み込まれるもの"
