    "row": 164,
    "rowsha": "vRyoHnOIguFesoLi9cdC+F1dYhyrAsaVqt9DlKyIWtI=",
    "originContent": "### Key Mechanisms",
    "translatedContent": "### 主要メカニズム"
  },
  {
    "row": 165,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 166,
    "rowsha": "aTsaO1xYlgfapCwfAOAWT2TqAMhs4kbWZ4o4MdUtCNw=",
    "originContent": "**Write Gate:** Filters out noise. Only behavior-changing facts, commitments, decisions, and explicit \"remember this\" requests pass through.",
    "translatedContent": "**書き込みゲート:** ノイズを除去します。行動を変える事実、約束、決定、および明示的な「これを覚えておいて」要求のみが通過します。"
  },
  {
    "row": 167,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 168,
    "rowsha": "jrXdLRvX+/jzaz47i1ctaNITTUWHALTkoM/q9paUrcI=",
    "originContent": "**Daily Log First:** All writes land in the daily log. Promotion to registers is a separate step, controlled by the user. This prevents the model from prematurely solidifying inferences.",
    "translatedContent": "**日次ログ優先:** すべての書き込みは日次ログに記録されます。レジスタへの昇格は別のステップで、ユーザーが制御します。これによりモデルが推論を早期に固定化するのを防ぎます。"
  },
  {
    "row": 169,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 170,
    "rowsha": "ffwLhHyJVkNpOdMKJ78bIC0wRDej3ETmI3x/uCsH2Fw=",
    "originContent": "**Contradiction Protocol:** Never silently overwrites. Old claims are marked `[superseded]` with date and reason. The pattern of change is preserved.",
    "translatedContent": "**矛盾プロトコル:** 静かに上書きしません。古い主張は日付と理由とともに`[superseded]`としてマークされます。変更のパターンは保持されます。"
  },
  {
    "row": 171,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 172,
    "rowsha": "kS5QBr/hkuZ23cdT5jKUljMrtRfsF8X7AUs7rDHfEv0=",
    "originContent": "**Correction Gate:** Human corrections get highest priority. One correction triggers writes to daily log + register + working memory.",
    "translatedContent": "**訂正ゲート:** 人間の訂正が最優先です。1回の訂正で日次ログ＋レジスタ＋作業メモリへの書き込みがトリガーされます。"
  },
  {
    "row": 173,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
