    "translatedContent": "### 他のメモリーツールとの比較"
  },
  {
    "row": 216,
    "rowsha": "897BWGvhJkjssY1V7veE0AEHWKUCLvQDKWnvuNiirv4=",
    "originContent": "### Compared to Other Memory Tools",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 217,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "|  | Total Recall | 自動取り込みツール |"
  },
  {
    "row": 218,
    "rowsha": "v35/Dpt0cRaYrXR9ElQYlpC0wLm5J9GJF7o8OX3rF6Q=",
    "originContent": "|  | Total Recall | Auto-ingest tools |",
    "translatedContent": "|---|---|---|"
  },
  {
    "row": 219,
    "rowsha": "I8ygK3TzhkY++iR5bHqQEbDSyT8MOLTRXV0nYgW1m0M=",
    "originContent": "|---|---|---|",
    "translatedContent": "| **保存されるもの** | 書き込みゲートを通過したもののみ | すべて |"
  },
  {
    "row": 220,
    "rowsha": "+Jgidzgz4+sYhHa2qo8wQpOF0J/Pv+Wio2iGxbewZqg=",
    "originContent": "| **What gets saved** | Only what passes the write gate | Everything |",
    "translatedContent": "| **デフォルトの保存先** | 日次ログ（後で昇格） | 永続ストレージ |"
  },
  {
    "row": 221,
    "rowsha": "hkLFNkAYYgTIZTAc9F/AuSQVUPLS9BEYs/ov/6l2rI8=",
    "originContent": "| **Default destination** | Daily log (promote later) | Permanent storage |",
    "translatedContent": "| **コンテキストコスト** | 約1500語の作業メモリ | 無制限に増加 |"
  },
  {
    "row": 222,
    "rowsha": "84bwm12giMc6pl0ZU9Kaxm7dDXMT5w4lnt+slI4e9Uk=",
    "originContent": "| **Context cost** | ~1500 words working memory | Grows unbounded |",
    "translatedContent": "| **修正** | 全階層に即時反映 | 変動あり |"
  },
  {
    "row": 223,
    "rowsha": "RSBPezDz+ZURr7s0JDV67WMJAu17cBvg0I8tKnZrbGY=",
    "originContent": "| **Corrections** | Propagate to all tiers immediately | Varies |",
    "translatedContent": "| **ユーザー制御** | 昇格は明示的 | 自動 |"
  },
  {
    "row": 224,
    "rowsha": "335TB00Rb3fLO4SprihfqzKWtHflfygN/6lPKp41JCU=",
    "originContent": "| **User control** | Promotion is explicit | Automatic |",
    "translatedContent": "| **アーキテクチャ** | メタデータ付き4層構造 | フラットまたは2層 |"
  },
  {
    "row": 225,
    "rowsha": "kftZXLOqpLaMyx4h719TuHiNySVqjbqKj4LYJxHJbaE=",
    "originContent": "| **Architecture** | 4-tier with metadata | Flat or 2-tier |",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 226,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "## プライバシー"
  },
  {
    "row": 227,
    "rowsha": "5CXxgd9sBe1fOQ1/F5SqqJHQp4uKbD07gsJwweuoKSk=",
    "originContent": "## Privacy",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 228,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "- すべてローカルで動作。ネットワークコールなし、テレメトリなし、外部サービスなし。"
  },
  {
    "row": 229,
    "rowsha": "YktrRZMZ4CvnwW72G1dKWxGpypUWqfL5VXewZ+IdMHU=",
    "originContent": "- Everything is local. No network calls, no telemetry, no external services.",
    "translatedContent": "- すべてのメモリは自分で読んだり編集したりできるプレーンなMarkdownファイル。"
  },
  {
    "row": 230,
    "rowsha": "WJ2h4LZb693v73JwbJiFgceX/ifhLW9sqAHr4UimCuk=",
    "originContent": "- All memory is plain markdown files you can read and edit yourself.",
    "translatedContent": "- `CLAUDE.local.md`はデフォルトでgitignoreされている（個人用）。"
  },
  {
    "row": 231,
    "rowsha": "C8lZfWZUjX2KGgN8UwH7g8CXkalQFEW52rcMtsKy5/A=",
    "originContent": "- `CLAUDE.local.md` is gitignored by default (it's personal).",
    "translatedContent": "- `memory/`もデフォルトでgitignoreされている（個人メモを含む可能性あり）。"
  },
  {
    "row": 232,
    "rowsha": "LII1Bbru4LNRYl9yd2Ze4qR3G4G9bbu+4kl5FMtgaEo=",
    "originContent": "- `memory/` is gitignored by default (it can contain personal notes).",
    "translatedContent": "- フックは会話のトランスクリプトを読み取らない。"
  },
  {
    "row": 233,
    "rowsha": "Gn/aRDB64vCHJ9ZCAmC34/Cdem3F3X5sFXTAtgmCHos=",
    "originContent": "- Hooks never read your conversation transcripts.",
    "translatedContent": "- 何が起きているか正確に知りたい場合は、`hooks/*.sh`と`memory/`を確認。すべてプレーンテキスト。"
  },
  {
    "row": 234,
    "rowsha": "M/0+KYFj0olMWuCfQL7g1GHl2SRSbGyI/v4dw0mtN3E=",
    "originContent": "- To see exactly what's happening: check `hooks/*.sh` and `memory/`. It's all plain text.",
    "translatedContent": "- アンインストールするには、`memory/`、`CLAUDE.local.md`、および`.claude/`のエントリ（または`/plugin uninstall recall`）を削除。"
  },
  {
    "row": 235,
    "rowsha": "kqmCFoHbalJh1kUcADmCfugCdkY+iEmRqUVRDhtzKkk=",
    "originContent": "- To uninstall: delete `memory/`, `CLAUDE.local.md`, and the `.claude/` entries (or `/plugin uninstall recall`).",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 236,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "## Superpowersとの併用"
  },
  {
    "row": 237,
    "rowsha": "Ik4HtlJKaj9zgSGgmdcfOiOMoYgoLvcx2SYmY5vRkps=",
    "originContent": "## Works Alongside Superpowers",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 238,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": "[Superpowers](https://github.com/obra/superpowers)を使用しても競合はありません。SuperpowersはClaudeの動作方法（方法論、TDD、計画）を管理し、Total RecallはClaudeが何を記憶するかを管理します。役割は異なりますが、同じプロジェクトです。"
  },
  {
    "row": 239,
    "rowsha": "+JJ8w32hnQL7DFlepWLw8xl1ZEbWI6r7cjCpG28PDEE=",
    "originContent": "If you use [Superpowers](https://github.com/obra/superpowers), there are no conflicts. Superpowers handles *how* Claude works (methodology, TDD, plans). Total Recall handles *what* Claude remembers. Different jobs, same project.",
